glom: glom (Database Design Tool)
glom:
glom: Glom is a database design tool, loosely based on FileMaker Pro, but 
glom: with a separate database server. Its simple framework should be enough 
glom: to implement most database applications. Glom has high-level features 
glom: such as relationships, lookups, related fields, related records, 
glom: calculated fields, drop-down choices, searching, reports, users and 
glom: groups. Glom uses the PostgreSQL database backend.
glom:
glom: Glom is open source software, released under the GPL License.
glom:
